mixin Delivery()
    section.delivery
        .container.delivery__container
            h2 How We Handle Delivery
            p We want to ensure that your experience with us is as smooth as possible. For delivery inquiries, please don’t hesitate to get in touch with us directly.
            div.card
                p.card-text.visible-text Delivery Areas
                p.card-text.hidden-text We currently provide delivery to select locations. To confirm if we can deliver to your area, please contact us directly for more details.
            div.card
                p.card-text.visible-text Delivery Times
                p.card-text.hidden-text Delivery times vary based on your location. We’ll provide you with an estimated delivery window when you reach out to us.
            div.card
                p.card-text.visible-text Delivery Costs
                p.card-text.hidden-text Delivery costs are based on your location and the size/weight of the products. For specific pricing, we encourage you to get in touch with our team.
            div.card
                p.card-text.visible-text Customer Assistance
                p.card-text.hidden-text If you need any help or have questions regarding delivery, our team is here to assist you. Feel free to reach out, and we’ll guide you through everything.
